此外，[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]足球俱樂部[[小保加體育會|博卡青年]]的球衣色彩採用與瑞典國旗一致的藍黃兩色，這一舉動源於1906年，當時博卡青年隊將球衣顏色從之前的黑白改為第一艘駛入博卡區港口的輪船所懸掛的旗幟色彩，而駛入博卡港口的第一艘輪船正是從哥本哈根駛來的瑞典貨輪。<ref>{{cite web |author=Georgina Turner and James Dart |url=http://football.guardian.co.uk/theknowledge/story/0,13854,1643916,00.html |title=Turner, Georgina & Dart, James. "Nicking the shirts off their backs," ''The Guardian'' (London, UK), Wednesday 23 November 2005 |publisher=Football.guardian.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2013-05-05 |archive-date=2008-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080320093647/http://football.guardian.co.uk/theknowledge/story/0,13854,1643916,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

